{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358020/extras/library_logo_transparent.png?t=1736563321\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ascend to the heavens and challenge the divine in <i>Olympus of the Heavens</i>, a fast-paced action RPG where you battle the mightiest Olympian gods in a realm above the clouds. Step into a mythical world filled with breathtaking temples, dynamic combat, and endless opportunities to forge your own path to power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Defy the Gods:</strong> Embark on a journey to overthrow the 12 Olympian gods, each residing in unique, intricately designed temples. Face epic boss battles where skill, strategy, and timing are your greatest allies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Claim the Divine Flames:</strong> As you defeat the gods, seize their sacred flames and use them to fuel your own power. Ignite your personal flame and ascend to become a force beyond the divine.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Deep Customization:</strong> Tailor your playstyle with an expansive skill tree, a wide variety of equipment, and powerful artifacts. Whether you prefer close combat, ranged attacks, or magical destruction, you can build a character that reflects your strategy.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Loot and Progression:</strong> Explore the temples and the floating lands surrounding them, filled with hidden treasures, powerful gear, and secrets waiting to be uncovered. Upgrade your weapons, armor, and abilities to take on even the most challenging foes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>A World Above the Clouds:</strong> Immerse yourself in a stunning isometric world where every temple is a reflection of its god's domain. From Zeus's stormy sanctuaries to Hades's shadowy fortress, each location is crafted with care and brimming with lore.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Fast-Paced Combat:</strong> Engage in visceral battles with responsive controls and fluid animations. Chain together devastating combos, dodge deadly attacks, and adapt to each god's unique fighting style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358020/extras/menu1.jpg?t=1736563321\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">In <i>Olympus of the Heavens</i>, the gods hold the skies, but the power to rise above them lies within you. Will you ignite your flame and claim your place among the legends? The heavens await your challenge!</h2>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358020/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736563321","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358020/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1736563321","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358020/22883da039d7c0757996adabf45c33c1c531606e/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736563321","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358020/22883da039d7c0757996adabf45c33c1c531606e/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736563321","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"LAN Co-op","id":48},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":"The game contains mild depictions of violence, such as blood effects when hitting enemies, and some suggestive content. Characters wear undergarments when their armor is removed, but there is no nudity or explicit sexual content."},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"htt